          .text-left
            img alt="Workflow Footprint" width="170px" height="350px" style="float:right" src=image_path("e-document-symphony.png")
          p.lead.m32.pb32 Invoices and other documents are scanned and uploaded onto Symphony. This prevents the risk of losing physical documents and allows for easier access for anyone that wants to verify or double check on the relevant documents, ultimately saving time as they do not need to check back on heaps of files to get the relevant data.
          p.lead.m32.pb32 This electronic documents will also enable them to capture early payment discounts and minimize late payments as they will not have a situation whereby invoices go missing.


